# regexly project rules (table of contents)

This project follows the rules defined in the files below. When editing or adding code, adhere to these rules.

| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| comments-english.mdc | All source comments and docs in English |
| extensibility.mdc | Extensibility design, interfaces, anyOf/not etc. |
| tree-shaking.mdc | File-level exports, barrel re-exports, sideEffects |
| framework-agnostic.mdc | Pure functions, framework-agnostic code |
| api-and-implementation.mdc | API table, ok() combined regex, report() per-predicate execution |

Refer to each file for details. Update the relevant rule file when new conventions or edge cases are agreed during implementation.
